Graz is [[Twin towns and sister cities|twinned]] with:&lt;ref name=&quot;Graz&quot;&gt;{{cite web |url=https://www.graz.at/cms/beitrag/10036153/7771861/Staedtepartnerschaften.html |title=Partner cities - City of Graz |publisher=www.graz.at |accessdate=21 August 2018 }}&lt;/ref&gt;

