* {{flagdeco|NOR}} [[Trondheim]], Norway, since 1968&lt;ref name=&quot;Graz&quot;/&gt;&lt;ref name=&quot;Trondheim&quot;&gt;{{in lang|no}}[http://www.trondheim.com/content.ap?thisId=93081934 Trondheims offisielle nettsted – Vennskapsbyer] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927054554/http://www.trondheim.com/content.ap?thisId=93081934 |date=27 September 2011 }}&lt;/ref&gt;
